snippet.title: STARVEIL PROTOCOL A.A.A. English demo is now available on Itch.io
snippet.description:
The English version of the Gamejam DEMO is now available for download on Itch.io!!

PLEASE NOTE:

The text for this English version was not official , and It will be quite different from the future full release.

I would like to thank an enthusiastic and noble friend, Kaychain, who did the entire English translation of this Demo. We were in agreement that this English version was kind of a fun project.

This version of the demo will remain as it was at Gamejam and will not be updated. Future multi-language releases will be handled by the publisher, so please keep an eye on our Steam page.

e.g. Music / Instrumental by Aries Beats
